<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/28686965-the-tunnels"><img alt="The Tunnels: Escapes Under the Berlin Wall and the Historic Films the JFK White House Tried to Kill" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1467923143l/28686965._SX98_.jpg" />
